        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; margin-top: 3rem;">
            <div>
                <h3>20+ Years Serving Central California</h3>
                <p>For over two decades, Monterey Bay Door has been a trusted name in Central California's commercial construction industry. Founded in 2007 with 30+ years of prior construction experience, we bring deep knowledge of project timelines, building requirements, and the real-world demands of commercial installations.</p>

                <h3>Local Expertise, Professional Standards</h3>
                <p>As a family-owned business based in Hollister, we understand the Central California market. We know the building codes, the local contractors, and the unique challenges of coastal construction. But we maintain the same professional standards and vendor relationships as the largest national distributors.</p>

                <h3>Direct Vendor Partnerships</h3>
                <p>As a direct partner with all vendors under the ASSA Abloy umbrella and other major manufacturers, we offer competitive pricing typically reserved for large national distributors. This means better prices for you and direct access to technical support when you need it.</p>
            </div>
